{'id': '970247890', 'text': "Wow, thank you so much for your incredible review! We're absolutely thrilled to hear that you had such a fantastic experience with us. Anju will be over the moon to know that his service made your stay extra special, and we couldn’t agree more his energy and vibe are amazing!

We’re delighted that you loved the hotel and the food as well. We can't wait to welcome you back for more unforgettable moments!

", 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-09-18', 'responder': 'General Manager', 'connectionToSubject': 'General Manager'}

{'id': '970248131', 'text': "Thank you for taking the time to share your experience with us. We’re glad to hear that you enjoyed a comfortable stay and found the rooms spacious and relaxing amidst the serene surroundings.

We appreciate your feedback regarding the dining options. We understand how important it is to cater to diverse tastes, and we'll definitely look into expanding our menu, particularly for Indian vegetarian, chicken, and lamb options. We’re also happy to know you enjoyed our selection of confectionery!

We hope to welcome you back for an even better experience in the future.", 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-09-18', 'responder': 'General Manager', 'connectionToSubject': 'General Manager'}

{'id': '970248361', 'text': 'Thank you for sharing your feedback with us. We’re delighted to hear that you enjoyed the stunning views from your room and the poolside dining experience! It’s great to know that our spacious rooms and comfortable beds added to your comfort, and that our team made you feel welcome with their helpful and friendly service.

We apologize for the inconvenience you experienced with the bathroom and hot water, but we’re glad it was resolved quickly. Your feedback is valuable, and we’ll be addressing the bathroom issue to ensure a more pleasant experience for future guests.

We hope to welcome you back soon for another relaxing stay with even more improvements!', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-09-18', 'responder': 'General Manager', 'connectionToSubject': 'General Manager'}

{'id': '970248894', 'text': 'Thank you for your lovely review! We’re delighted to hear that Anju made your dining experience so enjoyable with his friendly and welcoming service. It’s also fantastic that you enjoyed the delicious, generously portioned dishes, even with a bit of spice!

We truly appreciate your recommendation and look forward to welcoming you back for another memorable meal soon!
', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-09-18', 'responder': 'General Manager', 'connectionToSubject': 'General Manager'}

{'id': '970249457', 'text': 'Thank you so much for sharing your experience with us! We’re honored that you chose Earls Regent to celebrate your mother’s 80th birthday, and we’re delighted to hear that we could make the occasion memorable for you and your family.

It’s wonderful to know that Udari Sethunga and the banquets team provided exceptional service and attended to every detail, even under challenging circumstances. We’ll be sure to pass on your special thanks to Udari and the entire team.

Thank you once again for your kind words and for recommending us. We look forward to the opportunity to welcome you back for future celebrations!', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-09-18', 'responder': 'General Manager', 'connectionToSubject': 'General Manager'}

{'id': '970250703', 'text': 'Thank you for your excellent review! We’re thrilled to hear that you had such a positive experience with us, especially with the hospitality provided by Thilina and Umesh. It’s great to know that you enjoyed the tasty food, the good views, and the live music.

We’re delighted that you found our hotel a good choice while in Jaffna and that it will be your destination in Kandy for future business trips. Your recommendation to friends and relatives means a lot to us!

We look forward to welcoming you back soon.', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-09-18', 'responder': 'General Manager', 'connectionToSubject': 'General Manager'}

{'id': '970250786', 'text': 'Thank you for your wonderful review! We’re delighted to hear that you were pleasantly surprised by our breakfast, despite any initial skepticism. It’s fantastic to know you enjoyed the variety and quality of the options, including the mushrooms, breads, and bacon and eggs.

We’re also thrilled that our staff made a positive impression with their attentiveness and kindness. Your feedback means a lot to us, and we’re grateful for the opportunity to exceed your expectations.

We look forward to welcoming you back for another enjoyable stay!', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-09-18', 'responder': 'General Manager', 'connectionToSubject': 'General Manager'}

{'id': '970250838', 'text': 'Thank you so much for your kind words and positive feedback! We’re thrilled to hear that you had a special experience with us and enjoyed the delicious and diverse food, as well as the quality of the rooms.

It’s wonderful to know that Isuru and the rest of our staff made such a positive impact on your stay. We truly appreciate your comments and are delighted to hear that you would choose our hotel again in the future.

Thank you once again for your appreciation, and we look forward to welcoming you back!', 'lang': 'en', 'publishedDate': '2024-09-18', 'responder': 'General Manager', 'connectionToSubject': 'General Manager'}
